Case Studies

CUBE has been implemented in different types of projects and for various use cases.

Fakeeh University Hospital's Digital Twin

A large hospital project in the Middle east utilized CUBE on-premise for facility management. The work orders, specification manuals, as-built drawings and other asset-related documents were linked to the assets within the BIM model and stored in a single platform on the cloud.

General Contractor based in USA

The client worked in the AEC industry and extensively used BIM and related technologies to execute their projects. The existing CDE used by them could not be customized as per their organization standards, nor were they economically feasible.
